      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 102,
      "message": "why do you need to call initializeTraceContext() twice? once here and once in CloudConfiguration.java\n...\nAfter looking at other files, I noticed that you are calling initializeTraceContext() many times, which does not seem to be the right approach.",
