    {
      "id": "c9de7f29_9be8c247",
      "file_path": "datafile-app-server/src/main/java/org/onap/dcaegen2/collectors/datafile/configuration/SchedulerConfig.java",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 102,
      "message": "Each fetching of VES events and processing these is here here defined as a task. In this case the DFC is the initiator of the task. \nPreviously each line in the log contained the same information. I do not think that can be useful.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 5072,
        "name": "Patrik Buhr",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "patrik.buhr@est.tech",
        "username": "PatrikBuhr"
      },
      "updated": "2019-04-04 14:34:52.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "8d82358a_481ebabe",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "1cc883a8_5ccbd86e",
      "file_path": "datafile-app-server/src/main/java/org/onap/dcaegen2/collectors/datafile/controllers/ScheduleController.java",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 61,
      "message": "It is a matter of definition.\nMy viewis thatthe task of startTask() is to start the DFC. \nEXIT is then done when the starting is completed (and not after the DFC is stopped). \nStopping is another task.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 5072,
        "name": "Patrik Buhr",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "patrik.buhr@est.tech",
        "username": "PatrikBuhr"
      },
      "updated": "2019-04-04 14:34:52.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "7898af2d_1143c7bb",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "54cd3140_eab02069",
      "file_path": "datafile-app-server/src/main/java/org/onap/dcaegen2/collectors/datafile/controllers/ScheduleController.java",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 73,
      "message": "I think the whole idea of the request ID is that the initiator of a use case generates this. Then it will be possible to follow this through the system. \n\nBy this I mean that the DFC initiates a used case by polling the MR. Not that these request_IDs are generated by start and never changed.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 5072,
        "name": "Patrik Buhr",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "patrik.buhr@est.tech",
        "username": "PatrikBuhr"
      },
      "updated": "2019-04-04 14:34:52.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "27ca3868_3c28b3df",
      "unresolved": false
    },
